<p>
<lb n="1"/>© śrīmatu yādavanārāyaṇaṁ
<lb n="2"/>bhujabaḷapratāpacakravartti śrīsiṁhaṇadē<unclear>va</unclear>
<lb n="3"/>varṣada 39 neya viśvāsusaṁvatsarada
<lb n="4"/>Āśāḍa su 5 bri sankramāṇa bitīpātadaṁ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>du ma<unclear>llū</unclear>rageṟege śrīmatu lakṣmīpāḷadēvara
<lb n="6" break="no"/>sara sarvvādhikāri vi<unclear>ṭha</unclear>paṁḍitaru jōvidēvarasaru
<lb n="7"/>Eṁṭu gavuḍugaḷuṁ vūriṁ teṁkaṇa haḷḷiya hola
<lb n="8"/>haḷḷadiṁ mūḍalu Ere kaṁ 50 maṁ biṭṭaru
<lb n="9"/>maṁgaḷa mahāśrī yī dharmmamanaḷipidāta paṁcamahā
<lb n="10" break="no"/>pātakanaku <g type="ddanda">.</g>
</p>

